n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOENCD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOENCD6.png&h=3f236ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ytgkdcq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtgkdcq.png&h=29148297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2Oyyc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2Oyyc0.jpg&h=c64a4576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRGTx1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRGTx1F.jpg&h=c494c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「童心向党　健康成长」</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣由六歲去到廿八歲</span>，</span><br />\n咁你話深唔深紅（深藍絲）？"},{"pid":"bb372deb58554063c5803bf1d347d4c28d90129b","tid":1863273,"uid":229262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"唔好癲，你覺得終國vs俄國vs北韓vs古巴vs中東各國，邊個會最短命？"},{"pid":"af00747597e8ed8af31f3d19576464bf2f6201c4","tid":1863273,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"蘇聯先係真正勁果個"},{"pid":"cd9ae84c00b18703fb156c526da814b027ade24a","tid":1863273,"uid":78613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"其實大陸人咁多年黎都好享受弱者角色<br />\n成日話人歧視 恰佢地 黎講番自我點自強<br />\n一個極度鐘意自慰既民族"},{"pid":"46b402c8134c7358e110a32839f0a2c8647c8e2d","tid":1863273,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9978727c790cd30ebb711b23920f1a507f407a","tid":1863273,"uid":318069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"因為中共玩感性，同埋佢地係豬<br />\n食得飽就ok<br />\n大家要小心下下講感性既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"好似香港人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.g